title: Stade de Marchan
text: Stade de Marchan is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Tangier">Tangier</a>, <a href="Morocco">Morocco</a>. It is used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and used to be the home ground of <a href="IR%20Tanger">IR Tanger</a>. The stadium holds 14,000 people. It was however replaced by <a href="Stade%20de%20Tanger">Stade de Tanger</a> after the latter's construction was over.
